<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Your Parcel Has Been Delivered</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa; color: #000000;">

  <div style="background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.1);">
    <h2 style="color: #800020;">Delivery Successful!</h2>

    <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
      Hello <strong><%= senderName %></strong>,
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
      Weâ€™re happy to let you know that your parcel with Tracking ID <strong><%= trackingId %></strong> has been successfully delivered to <strong><%= recipientName %></strong>.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
      Thank you for trusting <strong><%= appName %></strong> with your delivery. You can view the delivery details by clicking the button below:
    </p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="<%= parcelDetailsUrl %>" 
         style="display: inline-block; background-color: #800020; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;">
        View Parcel Details
      </a>
    </div>

    <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
      If you have any questions or concerns, our support team is here for you.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
      Warm regards,<br />
      The <strong><%= appName %></strong> Team
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d; margin-top: 30px; text-align: center;">
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.
  </div>

</body>
</html>
